    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are acceptable at this risk level per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The observational study provides extensive corroborative evidence across five operating points, with RH < 1.0 and NIH deviations within ±11% at all conditions. The assessment team is satisfied that the CFD model has sufficient credibility to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
